        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-justify md:w-2/3">
          Dedicated to providing high-quality care for vulnerable and at risk
          children.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gun-metal-light text-justify md:w-2/3">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Pellentesque egestas risus
          netus etiam. Ac fringilla sed sollicitudin et tellus. Tempor
          scelerisque vehicula semper elit egestas in sollicitudin scelerisque
          arcu.
        </p>
        <Image alt="Happy Teenagers" src={ourHistoryImage1} />
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 md:flex md:flex-col md:items-center">
        <Image alt="Happy Teenagers" src={ourHistoryImage2} />
        <p class="text-gun-metal-light text-justify md:w-2/3">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Pellentesque egestas risus
